
CarBox is a kit to convert bicycles or motorcycles into four wheeled vehicles.

roll-cage, seat, steering wheel, brakes and other controls.

Two similar bikes are clamped to both sides of 

either side and the powertrain is joined in one of many ways.

Different sizes for different applications.



Options to put clutch, accelerator and gear-shifting on the steering-wheel or on the floor.


Remove the engine and transmission from one of the motorcycles.




Recycled version could be joined pieces of old frames.
Wood or bamboo could be used in some cases.
